import { Grid, Card, Typography } from '@mui/material'

export default function UserForm() {
	return (
		<Grid container 
			  direction="column"
			  alignItems="center"
			  justifyContent="center"
			  >
			<Grid item xs={3}>
				<Card 
				 sx={{mt:5}}
				>
					<Typography variant='filled'>
						Create User
					</Typography>
				</Card>
			</Grid>
		</Grid>
	)
}
